"The importance of fitting dust evolution models. We stress the
importance of actually fitting, in a consistent way, dust evolu-
tion models, rather than simply performing visual comparisons.
Here, we have attempted to fit M?, Mgas, Mdust, Z and SFR for
each galaxy. This rigorous process highlights the model limi-
tations. Most past studies have merely overlaid tracks on their
data, producing a convincing but inconsistent interpretation. For
instance, De Vis et al. (2017b), who used the same dust evolu-
